isciplines</span><hr size=1> Warriors have several of what I call &quot;give and take&quot; disciplines: Evasive, Defensive, Precision, and Aggressive.  With these disciplines, the warrior gets something, but then has to give up something.  For example with defensive, he takes less damage, but he also dishes out less.<br>
<br>
I was wondering has anyone figured out what the percentages are on the give and take of these disciplines?  For example, I once heard that with defensive, the warrior takes 50% less damage, while dishing out 40% less.  Is this accurate?  And what about evasive, precision, and aggressive?  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=iskandaralazeem>Iskandar Alazeem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guardian of the Battlefield</BR>STEEL WARRIOR Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 1131<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/15/03 9:49:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2917.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Questions about the &quot;Give and Take&quot; Discipline</span><hr size=1> Defensive is 40%/40%. Aggressive is 20%/20%, I believe. Not totally sure about evasive and precise. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tashant>Tashant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 35<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/15/03 10:05:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2917.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Questions about the &quot;Give and Take&quot; Discipline</span><hr size=1> see <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessage?topicID=1656.topic">pub14.ezboard.com/ftheste...1656.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> for info on defensive. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=l